title: Raymond James' Starner on Women in Financial Industry (Audio)

description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Margaret Starner, Senior Vice President, Financial Planning, at the Starner Group of Raymond James, can discuss women investors and advisers, Holistic financial planning, and behavioral finance.
